---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Celestra" description="Learn about Celestra, the premium RSS reader designed for iOS 26">
  <section class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Celestra</h1>
      <div class="content">
        <p class="intro">
          Celestra is a premium RSS reader designed exclusively for iOS 26,
          bringing the elegance of Liquid Glass design to your daily reading experience.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
          In an age of algorithmic feeds and attention-grabbing notifications,
          we believe in returning control to readers. RSS represents the open webâ€”a
          place where you choose what to read, when to read it, and how to organize your content.
        </p>

        <h2>Built for iOS 26</h2>
        <p>
          Celestra takes full advantage of iOS 26's revolutionary Liquid Glass design system,
          creating an immersive reading experience that feels native to the platform. Every
          interaction is crafted with care, from smooth animations to thoughtful typography.
        </p>

        <h2>Premium & Private</h2>
        <p>
          No ads. No tracking. No compromises. Celestra is a one-time purchase that respects
          your privacy and attention. Your reading habits are yours alone, synced securely
          via iCloud.
        </p>

        <div class="cta">
          <a href="/testflight" class="button">Join the TestFlight Beta</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .content {
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    background: #6366f1;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .button:hover {
    background: #4f46e5;
  }
</style>
